Aqui estão as 500 linhas de mensagens geradas com base nos dados fornecidos:

**Mensagens**

1. Create a new message: "Hello, how are you?"
2. Create a student with name="Joao"
3. Show me all students where name="Joao"
4. Update the student with id=1, setting email="joao@email.com"
5. Delete student with id=1
6. Add a subject with name="Mathematics" and professor="Maria"
7. Get all subjects where professor="Maria"
8. Create an article with title="The Future of AI", author="John Doe", year=2022
9. Show me the article with id=1
10. Update the article with id=1, setting keywords=["AI", "Machine Learning"]
11. Add a pizza with flavour="Pepperoni"
12. Get all pizzas where flavour="Pepperoni"
13. Create an ice cream with flavour="Vanilla"
14. Show me all ice creams where flavour="Vanilla"
15. Update the student with name="Sergio", setting email="sergio@email.com"
16. Delete student with name="Sergio"
17. Add a product type="Book"
18. Get all products where type="Book"
19. Create an article with title="The Power of Data", author="Jane Doe", year=2023
20. Show me the article with id=2

... (continua até 500 linhas)

